summary: Hi! Can I have a male My Hero Academia match up please? I'm a girl that's kind, innocent, intelligent, curious, and shy. I’m a...
question: Hi! Can I have a male My Hero Academia match up please? I'm a girl that's kind, innocent, intelligent, curious, and shy. I’m a pretty accepting person and one of my main goals is to push people to do what makes them happy, in terms of job, religion, sexuality, etc. I love writing, singing, and dancing, but I’m too shy to perform in front of others. I'm more into writing horror and murder mysteries, which is a big contrast to my “be nice to everyone” mentality. (1/3)
answer:
I listen to a wide range of punk, rock, alternative, and pop. I enjoy making people happy and making sure everyone is smiling. I’m a bit of an old soul. I love going out and taking pictures with my polaroid (usually alone-I get embarrassed around others) or listening to music. I’m a Gryffindor and an INFJ if that helps anything. When it comes to flirting I get really flustered, but if you playfully make fun of or (2/3)

tease me I can retaliate and it actually helps to get me out of my shell. I have really big grey/green eyes, wear thick floral-rimmed glasses, and have longish blonde hair. I’m 5'7" and relatively thin, but I still have a bit of extra pudge I’d like to get off. Finally, I have imperfect teeth that I get embarrassed about on occasion, but I tend to smile a lot so over the years I’ve gotten over it except for the occasional moment when I don’t have the highest self-esteem. Thank you! (3/3)

Thank you for the request! Your glasses seem really cool, I don’t think I’ve ever seen floral ones!

I match you with…

Shouto Todoroki!

I also see Shouto as a bit of an older soul. Your happy nature helps to get him a little bit out of his shell, and makes him more optimistic about things in general. He was totally shocked when he found out about your horror writings, but he’s really more impressed than creeped out. He will help to push you to have a better self-esteem while you push him to be happier. 


I hope you liked your matchup! - Mod Bunny

Requests are open!

trail.content:
I listen to a wide range of punk, rock, alternative, and pop. I enjoy making people happy and making sure everyone is smiling. I’m a bit of an old soul. I love going out and taking pictures with my polaroid (usually alone-I get embarrassed around others) or listening to music. I’m a Gryffindor and an INFJ if that helps anything. When it comes to flirting I get really flustered, but if you playfully make fun of or (2/3)

tease me I can retaliate and it actually helps to get me out of my shell. I have really big grey/green eyes, wear thick floral-rimmed glasses, and have longish blonde hair. I’m 5'7" and relatively thin, but I still have a bit of extra pudge I’d like to get off. Finally, I have imperfect teeth that I get embarrassed about on occasion, but I tend to smile a lot so over the years I’ve gotten over it except for the occasional moment when I don’t have the highest self-esteem. Thank you! (3/3)

Thank you for the request! Your glasses seem really cool, I don’t think I’ve ever seen floral ones!

I match you with…

Shouto Todoroki!

I also see Shouto as a bit of an older soul. Your happy nature helps to get him a little bit out of his shell, and makes him more optimistic about things in general. He was totally shocked when he found out about your horror writings, but he’s really more impressed than creeped out. He will help to push you to have a better self-esteem while you push him to be happier. 


I hope you liked your matchup! - Mod Bunny
